483
00:27:13,299 --> 00:27:14,567
Tudo bem, Anthony,
colocar as cargas.

484
00:27:14,567 --> 00:27:16,169
A sala de comando
deveria ser por ali.

485
00:27:16,169 --> 00:27:17,404
